<li>DSA 913: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-913">gdk-pixbuf</a> &ndash;
    Mehrere Verwundbarkeiten.</li>
<li>DSA 914: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-914">horde2</a> &ndash;
